    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>It uses <a href=\"http://www.jcp.org/en/jsr/detail?id=269\" rel=\"noreferrer\">JSR 269 Pluggable Annotation Processing API</a> available in Java 6.</p>\n\n<p>Note that <code>lombok.jar</code> contains a file named <code>/META-INF/services/javax.annotation.processing.Processor</code>. When <code>javac</code> sees this file in a compilation classpath, it runs annotation processors defined there during compilation.</p>\n"
