      "body" : "Is Lombok still using internal APIs or has this situation changed since 2011? <a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/java/comments/6ilt97/what_do_you_think_of_project_lombok/dj7e5l4/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">This comment</a> claims that Lombok uses official APIs these days."
